        "title": "Summary",
        "content": "| Priority | Files | Effort | ROI |\n|----------|-------|--------|-----|\n| 1 -- Pure logic | `LiteralMode`, `SovereignRouter`, `KnowledgeGraphService` | ~4h | Very high |\n| 2 -- Core state | `ExecutiveSpine`, `HistoryOfThought`, `EventBus` | ~12h | High |\n| 3 -- Services | `RewriteService`, `BriefService`, `ChatService` | ~20h | High |\n| 4 -- Integration | EventBus→Vault, Ollama fallback | ~8h | Medium |\n| 5 -- Components | `LinearCanvas`, `SteeringDrawer`, `AskAura` | ~30h | Medium |\n\n**Start with Priority 1** -- the three pure-function modules have no async, no DOM, no IndexedDB dependencies. The test skeletons above can run immediately after installing `@testing-library/react`.",
